cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to correct perspective distortion in portrait photographs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with graphics and image manipulation, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
